1071203.simpleDesc:
When in the <material=underline c=#FFFFFF h=2 event=terminology args=(107101)>Still stance</material>: This skill is replaced by Eternal Prosperity: Wind. Skill may only be cast when Divine Grace is at max, dealing Wind DMG. Mod switches to the <material=underline c=#FFFFFF h=2 event=terminology args=(107102)>Move stance</material>, removes all <material=underline c=#FFFFFF h=2 event=terminology args=(107103)>Nay</material> Marks, resets the CD of Eternal Prosperity: Thunder, and summons <material=underline c=#FFFFFF h=2 event=terminology args=(107105)>Thundercloud Strikes</material> to attack targets, dealing Thunder DMG. Switches to the <material=underline c=#FFFFFF h=2 event=terminology args=(107101)>Still stance</material> when Divine Grace is at 0.
When in the <material=underline c=#FFFFFF h=2 event=terminology args=(107102)>Move stance</material>: This skill is replaced by Eternal Prosperity: Thunder. Expends Divine Grace to deal DMG over three strikes, with the final strike summoning some <material=underline c=#FFFFFF h=2 event=terminology args=(107105)>Thundercloud Strikes</material> in the area ahead. Depending on when Aero Break is cast alternately with this skill, four follow-on sword moves occur, and each dealing different damage.
Move 1: Casting Aero Break directly;
Move 2: Casting Aero Break before the second strike;
Move 3: Casting Aero Break before the third strike;
Move 4: Casting Aero Break before both the second and third strikes.
